      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved over the years, so it's totally ready for its next big adventure with you! Everything runs smoothly, the seats are super comfy, and it still looks great parked in the driveway. If you're looking for a reliable, happy car that won't let you down, this is definitely the one. Drop me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2008 Porsche 911 Carrera (997.1) featuring the 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six powerplant. This M96/05 engine is paired with a 6-speed G97/01 manual transaxle, offering a mechanical connection lost in modern iterations. The vehicle features a recent IMS bearing retrofit and rear main seal replacement, addressing common platform concerns. The chassis utilizes Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) to regulate damping rates, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear geometry remain composed under high lateral G-loads. Braking is handled by four-piston monobloc calipers over ventilated, cross-drilled rotors, providing exceptional thermal management. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain is synchronized for immediate throttle response and peak longitudinal performance.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Reliable performance. Clean title.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a discerning buyer looking for a reliable and well-presented daily driver. The exterior finished in a classic metallic hue retains a high-gloss luster, though close inspection reveals minor road-wear consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin remains a comfortable sanctuary; the upholstery is free of tears or significant stains, and all interior electronics\u2014including the premium audio system and navigation\u2014are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health, having undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection and a recent fluid service. It shifts smoothly, brakes firmly, and the suspension provides a quiet, composed ride. We have maintained a detailed service history, confirming that all scheduled maintenance has been performed on time. This is a turn-key vehicle that offers a premium driving experience without the new-car price tag. Sold with a clean title and two sets of keys.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Demonstrating consistent mechanical integrity and a well-preserved aesthetic, it offers a refined driving experience that balances performance with long-term reliability. All systems have been rigorously evaluated to ensure they meet our standards for safety and operational excellence. This is a distinguished choice for those who demand quality and value in equal measure.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It's in solid condition, runs super smooth, and has been well-loved and looked after. If you're looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one for you! I\u2019d love for it to go to a great new home, so feel free to reach out and come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superb driver-spec example of the high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six pulls hard to its 8,000 RPM redline, benefiting from a recent valve adjustment and a refreshed VANOS system. Power is managed through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and sent to the rear wheels via a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis remains composed thanks to upgraded polyurethane bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers, while the critical rear subframe mounting points have been inspected and reinforced. Finished in Carbon Black, the exterior shows a light, honest patina, while the mechanical vitals remain at peak operating temperature even under load. A performance-oriented classic ready for the backroads.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
